[The statement by the ministerial health authorities of a country -- rather
than another source within the same country -- should be authentic,
reliable and authoritative. The current official announcement by Health and
Social Development Vice-Minister of Venezuela was meant to correct the
inaccurate death figures given recently by the Mayor of Guanare (see also:
20051022.3082) - Mod.RY]
